## Drag

Choices can now take a `drag` property. This will make list items "draggable" and allow you to drag/drop to copy files from your machine (or even from URLs!) into any app. When using remote URLs, their will be a bit of "delay" while the file downloads (depending on the file size) between "drag start" and "drop enabled", so just be aware. I'll add some sort of download progress indicator sometime in the future, just not high priority ðŸ˜…

```js
// Menu: Drag demo

await arg(
  {
    placeholder: "Drag something from below",
    ignoreBlur: true,
  },
  [
    {
      name: "Heart Eyes (local)",
